Commerce supports entrepreneurship in Haiti - HaitiLibre.com : Haiti news 7/7|url=http://www.haitilibre.com/en/news-9956-haiti-economy-the-ministry-of-commerce-supports-entrepreneurship-in-haiti.html|website=HaitiLibre.com|accessdate=22 December 2016}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* {{illm|List of Commerce ministers of Haiti|fr|Liste des ministres ha\u00eftiens du Commerce}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Ministries of Haiti}}\n\n\n{{Haiti-stub}}\n\n\n[[Category:Government ministries of Haiti|Commerce]]\n[[Category:Economy ministries|Haiti]]\n[[Category:Economy of Haiti]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox government agency\n| agency_name     = Ministry of Commerce and Industry\n| type            = \n| nativename      = \n| nativename_a    = \n| nativename_r    = \n| seal            = \n| seal_width      = \n| seal_caption    = \n| logo            = Coat of arms of Haiti.svg\n| logo_width      = 100px\n| logo_caption    = Coat of arms of Haiti\n| picture         = \n| picture_width   = \n| picture_caption = \n| formed          = <!-- {{Start date|YYYY|MM|DD}} OR {{Start date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| preceding1      = \n| preceding2      = <!-- up to |preceding6= -->\n| dissolved       = \n| superseding     = \n| agency_type     =\n| jurisdiction    = [[Haiti|Republic of Haiti]]\n| headquarters    = \n| coordinates     = <!-- {{coord|LATITUDE|LONGITUDE|type:landmark_region:US|display=inline,title}} -->\n| motto           = \n| employees       = \n| budget          = \n| minister1_name  = Wilson Laleau\n| minister1_pfo   = \n| minister2_name  = \n| minister2_pfo   = <!-- up to |minister7_name= -->\n| deputyminister1_name = \n| deputyminister1_pfo  = \n| deputyminister2_name = \n| deputyminister2_pfo  = <!-- up to |deputyminister7_name= -->\n| chief1_name     = \n| chief1_position = \n| chief2_name     = \n| chief2_position = <!-- up to |chief9_name= -->\n| parent_department = \n| parent_agency   = \n| child1_agency   = \n| child2_agency   = <!-- up to |child25_agency= -->\n