a]]\n*[[Astro Xiao Tai Yang]]\n===Radio===\nThe available [[FM broadcasting|FM]] [[radio station]]s in Ipoh, both [[public broadcasting|public]] (including Ipoh-based Perak FM) and [[commercial broadcasting|commercial]], are as listed below.\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Frequency\n!Station\n!Operator\n!Language\n|-\n|87.6&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[One FM]]||[[Media Prima]]||[[Chinese language|Chinese]] ([[Malaysian Mandarin|Mandarin]], [[Cantonese]])\n|-\n|87.9&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Fly FM]]||[[Media Prima]]||[[English language|English]], [[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|88.3&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting#|FM]]||[[Radio Klasik FM]]||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|88.5&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting#|FM]]||[[Nasional FM]]||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|90.1&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[TraXX FM]]||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[English language|English]]\n|-\n|90.9&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Nasional FM]]||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|92.1&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Ai FM]]||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[Chinese language|Chinese]] ([[Malaysian Mandarin|Mandarin]], Various [[Varieties of Chinese|Chinese dialects]])\n|-\n|92.7&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Hitz (radio station)|Hitz]]||[[Astro Radio]]||[[English language|English]]\n|-\n|94.3&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Mix (radio station)|Mix]]||[[Astro Radio]]||[[English language|English]]\n|-\n|95.6&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||Perak FM||[[Radio Televisyen Malaysia|RTM]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|96.0&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Suria FM]]||[[The Star (Malaysia)|Star Rfm]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|96.9&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Sinar (radio station)|Sinar]]||[[Astro Radio]]||[[Malay language|Malay]]\n|-\n|97.9&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Raaga (radio station)|Raaga]]||[[Astro Radio]]||[[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|-\n|98.5&nbsp;[[FM broadcasting|FM]]||[[Melody (radio 